        <mxCell id="z25E2ikE3pw0LlSkzHaf-1" parent="1" style="text;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" value="&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;Requesting Node          Satellite              Gateway                 NCC&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;(1) Auth Request         {$ID_{req}, N_a$}&lt;br/&gt;(2) Relay Request          {$ID_{req}, N_a, ID_s$}&lt;br/&gt;(3) Forward Request          {$ID_{req}, N_a, ID_s$}&lt;br/&gt;(4) Identity Verification        Generate Session Key $K_s, N_b, Cred$&lt;br/&gt;(5) Auth Response                  $\{K_s\}_{enc}, N_b, Cred$&lt;br/&gt;(6) Relay Response                                $\{K_s\}_{enc}, N_b, Cred$&lt;br/&gt;(7) Auth Response                      $\{K_s\}_{enc}, N_b, Cred$&lt;br/&gt;(8) Confirm &amp;amp; Key Derivation                    $MAC(N_a, N_b, ID_s)$&lt;br/&gt;(9) Encrypted Communication                         Protected Data Flow (using $K_s$)&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;Notation:&lt;br/&gt;- $ID_{req}$: Identity of requesting node&lt;br/&gt;- $ID_s$: Identity of satellite&lt;br/&gt;- $N_a, N_b$: Nonces&lt;br/&gt;- $K_s$: Session key&lt;br/&gt;- $\{K_s\}_{enc}$: Encrypted session key&lt;br/&gt;- $Cred$: Credentials&lt;br/&gt;- $MAC$: Message Authentication Code&lt;/font&gt;" vertex="1">
